  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Pneumostem® for IVH in Premature Infants (Phase 2a)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy and Safety Evaluation of Pneumostem® Versus a Control Group for Treatment of IVH in Premature Infants (Phase 2a)</official_title>
