  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to evaluate the efficacy and safety of a single
      intraventricular administration of Pneumostem® for treatment of Intraventricular hemorrhage
      (IVH) in high-risk premature infants by comparing Pneumostem-treated group with a control
      group.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
